# Pita Cigars

> Pita Cigars (Flor de Pita) is a family-owned cigar maker founded in 1968 by Arnaldo Laurencio, based in Miami, Florida. Every cigar is hand-rolled in Estelí, Nicaragua from aged Nicaraguan long-filler tobacco. Products are sold through brick-and-mortar retailers, not online. Tobacco products are intended for adults 21 years of age or older.

Factory and office: 1895 NW 21st St, Miami, FL 33142 · Phone: (305) 548-1212 · Email: pitacigars@att.net · Hours: Mon-Fri 9AM-5PM

